node.title: There’s A Promise That Produces Peace

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Steven Furtick on September 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'A PRAYER FOR ANYONE WHO FEELS ALONE TODAY: God open our eyes to the persistence of your presence today. Someone doesn't feel like you're present with them, but you are, you have been, and you always will be God, pray this day would be a day of awakening so we could know we never have to be alone not for one moment of our lives. In Jesús' name, AMEN.'.

node.text: God is with you - He always has been and He always will be. You are not alone.
